# Change rows to columns to have Places
as a column
def pivot_metadata(df):
df.index = [0] *
len(df)
return df.pivot(columns = 0,
values = 1)
metadata
= pd.DataFrame()
for df
in list_metadata:
new_df
= pivot_metadata(df)
metadata = pd.concat([metadata,
new_df])
metadata
